# Test fixtures

## failure-events.json

This file uses **mock config IDs** `"A"` and `"B"` for isolated unit tests. They are not production config IDs. Production configs in `configs/*.json` use IDs such as `"config-a"`, `"config-b"`, `"config-gemini"`, and `"config-manus"`. The short IDs here keep tests simple and independent of the actual config filenames.
